00:42:45,680 --> 00:42:48,240
Shit! What am I gonna do?

542
00:42:49,200 --> 00:42:52,240
Damn, the dorm security officer
is strict, too.

543
00:42:54,400 --> 00:42:56,200
Okay, I'm leaving.

544
00:42:57,040 --> 00:42:58,000
But…

545
00:42:59,600 --> 00:43:01,880
you wouldn't really
do anything to him, right?

546
00:43:04,880 --> 00:43:06,320
Just…

547
00:43:07,320 --> 00:43:08,640
go easy on him.

548
00:43:09,640 --> 00:43:11,160
