554
00:44:51,200 --> 00:44:52,760
you're just like…

555
00:44:54,520 --> 00:44:55,840
a child.

556
00:44:59,320 --> 00:45:00,640
But when you're awake…

557
00:45:02,880 --> 00:45:04,320
you're nothing but a brat.

558
00:46:04,960 --> 00:46:06,440
I want to see you…

559
00:46:08,400 --> 00:46:10,120
when you wake up…

560
00:46:11,600 --> 00:46:14,320
