562
00:47:00,640 --> 00:47:02,080
Sweet dreams.

563
00:47:03,680 --> 00:47:05,000
Roomie.

564
00:47:36,000 --> 00:47:38,760
{\an8}In case you're hungry, lick the bed.

565
00:47:40,760 --> 00:47:42,320
{\an8}Don't insult my dad!

566
00:47:44,840 --> 00:47:46,200
{\an8}Who took care of me?

567
00:47:46,680 --> 00:47:48,480
{\an8}You don't want it to be me, right?
